      Phase Agent_simple.argumentationCorePhase()
      Seventh phase of an argumentation, the Agent uses AMAIL to generate a new Intensional definition for a new Concept that would satisfy him and the Attacker.
      Phase Agent_simple.argumentationInitializeExtension()
      Sixth phase of an argumentation, the Agent creates the Extensional definitions for a new Concept that would lead to an agreement on the meaning.
      Phase Agent_simple.argumentationStartPhase()
      Fifth phase of an argumentation, the Discussion is created in order to reduce the number of disagreements.
      Phase Agent_simple.buildHypothesisPhase()
      Second phase of an argumenation, build a Hypothesis with the intensional definitions of this Agent (marked *) and the other Agent's ones (marked Â°), thanks to the Messages received during the initial phase.
      Phase Agent_simple.changeSignPhase()
      Tenth phase of an argumentation, the Agent might change the Signs of its Concepts according to the results of the vote that occured in the VoteForSignState.
      Phase Agent_simple.expressAgreementState()
      Third phase of an argumentation, the Agreement values for each couple of Concepts between this Agent's Concepts, and the other {code Agent}'s Concepts in the Hypothesis is sent to the other Agent.
      Phase Agent_simple.initialPhase()
      First phase of an argumentation, sends the intensional definitions of all the Concepts to the other Agent.
      Phase Agent_simple.modifyAgreementStatePhase()
      Fourth phase of an argumentation, the Agreement values for each couple of the Concepts evaluated during a expressAgreementState is modified, according to the values received from the other Agent.
      Phase Agent_simple.stop()
      The final Phase of the argumentation.
      Phase Agent_simple.turn()

      Phase Agent_simple.waitAgreementPhase()
      Eighth phase of an argumentation, the Agent adds/delets Concepts from its current ContrastSet.
